text: "Real Muthaphuckkin G's" (also known as "Real Compton City G's") is a song off American rapper Eazy-E's second EP, It's On (~~Dr. Dre~~) 187um Killa. The song was released on August 26, 1993. The song was a diss song towards former N.W.A member Dr. Dre and his protégé Snoop Doggy Dogg. On the Billboard charts, the song peaked at #42 on the Hot 100. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1993 songs Category:Diss tracks Category:Rap songs
